パッケージ com.shimizukenta.secs.local.property

インタフェース ObjectProperty<T>

型パラメータ:
T - Type
すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
Gettable<T>, ObjectGettable<T>, ObjectObservable<T>, ObjectSettable<T>, Observable<T>, Property<T>, java.io.Serializable, Settable<T>
public interface ObjectProperty<T>
extends Property<T>, ObjectGettable<T>, ObjectSettable<T>, ObjectObservable<T>
Object value Property, includes Getter, Setter, Observer.
  • To build instance, newInstance(Object)
  • To get value, ObjectGettable.get()
  • To get Optional, ObjectGettable.optional()
  • To set value, ObjectSettable.set(Object)
  • To detect value changed, Observable.addChangeListener(ChangeListener)
  • To compute,
    • ObjectObservable.computeIsEqualTo(ObjectObservable)
    • ObjectObservable.computeIsNotEqualTo(ObjectObservable)
  • To wait until condition is true,
    • ObjectObservable.waitUntilEqualTo(ObjectObservable)
    • ObjectObservable.waitUntilNotEqualTo(ObjectObservable)
    • ObjectObservable.waitUntilNotNullAndGet()
    • ObjectObservable.waitUntilNull()
関連項目:
ObjectGettable, ObjectSettable, ObjectObservable, Property
